### =============================
### 1️⃣ 卖家注册（动态用户名 - auto_ 前缀）
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "auto_seller_{{$timestamp}}",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "seller"
}

### =============================
### 2️⃣ 买家注册（动态用户名 - auto_ 前缀）
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "auto_buyer_{{$timestamp}}",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "buyer"
}

### =============================
### 3️⃣ 卖家登录（自动保存 token）
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "auto_seller_{{$timestamp}}",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {% client.global.set("seller_token", response.body.access_token); %}

### =============================
### 4️⃣ 卖家发布房源
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/property/
Authorization: Bearer {{seller_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Tokyo Apartment",
  "description": "Near station",
  "price": 120000,
  "location": "Tokyo"
}

### =============================
### 5️⃣ 房源详情
### =============================

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/property/1

### =============================
### 6️⃣ 房源列表（公开）
### =============================

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/property/

### =============================
### 7️⃣ 买家登录（自动保存 token）
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "auto_buyer_{{$timestamp}}",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {% client.global.set("buyer_token", response.body.access_token); %}

### =============================
### 8️⃣ 买家收藏房源
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/favorite/1
Authorization: Bearer {{buyer_token}}

### =============================
### 9️⃣ 查看我的收藏
### =============================

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/favorite/
Authorization: Bearer {{buyer_token}}

### =============================
### 🔟 卖家创建合同（注意：buyer_id=2 如果你清空过数据库请改成实际ID）
### =============================

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/contract/
Authorization: Bearer {{seller_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "property_id": 1,
  "buyer_id": 2,
  "price": 120000
}

### =============================
### 1️⃣1️⃣ 买家查看合同
### =============================

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/contract/
Authorization: Bearer {{buyer_token}}

### =============================
### 1️⃣2️⃣ 卖家查看合同
### =============================

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/contract/
Authorization: Bearer {{seller_token}}

### =============================
### 1️⃣3️⃣ 卖家完成合同
### =============================

PUT http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/contract/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{seller_token}}

### =============================
### 1️⃣4️⃣ 房源统计
### =============================

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/property/stats